.jumbotron
  .container
    .row.no-margin
      .col-lg-7
        %h2.header.hidden-md.hidden-lg
          Help cool projects grow.
        %h1.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
          Help cool projects grow.
        %h3
          Support project growth by contributing towards individual features and improvements.
          -#Support growing projects by crowdfunding individual features and improvements.
          -#Use donations, pledges, and votes to gauge user opinions.
      .col-lg-5
        .row
          %form.form-horizontal.ng-pristine.ng-valid.landing-sign-up{method: "post", "ng-submit" => "submit()", name: "f", "novalidate" => "", style:"margin-bottom:0;"}
            .form-group
              %div{style:"min-height:28px;"}
                .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
                  %span.alert-success.alert.fade{"ng-show" => "register_success && !errors", style:"padding:8px;font-size:18px;"}
                    All setup, thanks!
                  %span.alert-danger.alert.fade{"ng-show" => "errors", style:"padding:8px;font-size:18px;"}
                    %span{"ng-show" => "errors.length === 1"} {[{ errors[0] }]}
                    %span{"ng-show" => "error_header"} {[{ error_header }]}
                    %ul{"ng-show" => "errors.length > 1"}
                      %li{"ng-repeat" => "error in errors"} {[{error}]}
            .form-group{"valid-class" => "f.address"}
              .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
                %input.form-control.ng-pristine.ng-valid{"ng-model" => "address", name: "address", type: "email",
                placeholder:"Email", required: ""}
            .form-group
              .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
                %button.btn.btn-info.fill-link{type: "submit", "ng-disabled" => "!f.$valid"}
                  %i.fa.fa-edit
                  Register for updates
                %p.text-muted
                  By clicking "Register for updates", you agree to our
                  %a{href: "/tos", target: "_blank"} terms of service
                  and
                  %a{href: "/privacy", target: "_blank"} privacy policy
        .row
          .col-lg-10.col-lg-offset-1.text-center
            %hr.hr-header
        .row
          .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center.text-muted.no-gutter
            %a.twitter-follow-button{"data-size" => "large", "data-lang" => "en", "data-show-screen-name" => "true", "data-show-count" => "false", :href => "https://twitter.com/crowdlinkdotio"} Follow @crowdlinkdotio
            :javascript
              !function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,"script","twitter-wjs");

.row.no-margin
  .col-sm-12
    .row.share-padding
      .share-container
        %span.pull-left
          -# twitter share button
          %a{"twitter" => "", "data-text" => "Help cool projects grow", "data-via" => "crowdlinkdotio", "data-url" => "http://crowdlink.io"}
        %span.pull-left{style:"padding-right:24px;"}
          -# facebook share button
          .fb-share-button{"fbparse"=> "", "data-href" => "http://crowdlink.io", "data-type" => "button_count"}
        %span.pull-left
          .g-plus{"data-action" => "share", "data-annotation" => "bubble", "data-href" => "http://crowdlink.io"}
          / Place this tag after the last share tag.
          :javascript
            (function() {
              var po = document.createElement('script'); po.type = 'text/javascript'; po.async = true;
              po.src = 'https://apis.google.com/js/platform.js';
              var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(po, s);
            })();
.jumbotron.home-body
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.no-gutter
        .row
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3
                .text-center
                  %i.fa.fa-bullhorn.fa-3x
                  %br
                  Community driven
            .row
              %p
                Vote and make microdonations towards problems you'd like
                solved, or pledge money towards their completion.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3
                .text-center
                  %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.fa-3x
                  %br
                  Solve important problems
            .row
              %p
                Tell project owners which issues matter, and help motivate work
                being done in the most needed areas.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3
                .text-center
                  %i.fa.fa-group.fa-3x
                  %br
                  Microdonation based
            .row
              %p
                Support a project by giving as little as $0.01. Add funds to
                your account with a credit card or a bank transfer.
  .container.more-info
    .row
      .col-md-12.no-gutter.text-center
        %h4
          %div
            %span
              Learn more
              %i.fa.fa-angle-double-down
.jumbotron.comm-body
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.no-gutter
        .header
          %h2.title.hidden-md.hidden-lg
            %span.fa.fa-tachometer
            Feedback methods
          %h1.title.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
            %span.fa.fa-tachometer
            Feedback methods
        .row
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Pledges
            .row
              %p
                Endorse a Problem or Solution by promising to give an amount upon its
                successful implementation. Payment is held in escrow until the
                project owner marks the task complete.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Votes
            .row
              %p
                Upvote a Problem or Solution you'd like to see resolved to
                improve its visibility. Votes are completely free and appear
                alongside Pledges and Donations.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Donations
            .row
              %p
                Give a gift amount on a Problem or Solution that will be given
                regardless of implementation outcome. Help support the project
                and show your interest in specific areas at the same time.
.jumbotron.proj-body
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.no-gutter
        .header
          %h2.title.hidden-md.hidden-lg
            %span.fa.fa-sitemap
            Workflow
          %h1.title.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
            %span.fa.fa-sitemap
            Workflow
        .row
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Projects
            .row
              %p
                All Tasks and Suggestions are managed under the context of a
                single Project. Project owners control the disbursement of funds
                and can divide the payout between multiple users.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Tasks
            .row
              %p
                Tasks focus on a pain point that the user has with a product
                or service. Tasks may receive Donations, Votes or Pledges from
                any user and can be proposed by any user.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Suggestions
            .row
              %p
                A Task may have multiple Suggestions proposed for it.
                Suggestions can be endorsed in the same way as Tasks and can
                also be added by any user.
.jumbotron.acct-body
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.no-gutter
        .header
          %h2.title.hidden-md.hidden-lg
            %span.fa.fa-lock
            Finance details
          %h1.title.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
            %span.fa.fa-lock
            Finance details
        .row
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Accounts
            .row
              %p
                Each user has a Crowdlink account that maintains a running balance. Add funds to
                your account with a credit card, bank transfer, or from Donations
                and Pledges you receive. Account balances can be
                withdrawn from your Crowdlink account via bank transfer.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Network Fees
            .row
              %p
                Crowdlink charges a fee of 6% on funds moving between
                users via Pledges or Donations, regardless of amount. This fee is likely to change as our
                volume changes.
          .col-md-4
            .row
              %h3.text-center Processor Fees
            .row
              %p
                We use
                %a{href:"http://www.balancedpayments.com", target: "_blank"} Balanced Payments
                to allow you to use credit cards and bank accounts on Crowdlink.
                They charge various fees that may apply when depositing or withdrawing money from Crowdlink. Check our
                %a{"ng-click" => "help('fees')"} help
                for a more detailed explanation of those fees.
